what is TestNG?
TestNG provides advanced features such as annotations, data-driven testing, test sequencing,
and parallel testing to help you organize and execute your Selenium tests more efficient
and effectively.

TestNg--> Test Next Generation

TestNg is an 3rd party testing framework which uses annotations to test the web application and it can be
integrated with selenium

it provides full control over the test methods, test execution  , test classes

it produces in built html test reports

It allows you to run the test cases of a particular group

The main importance of the testng is Parallel execution of test cases which means we can test the test
cases in different browsers at a single time which means (cross browser testing)